    <img width="200px" height="200px" class="image2" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0788/1821/4221/files/2.jpg?v=1707486871" alt="Description of the image">
    <img width="200px" height="200px" class="image3" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0788/1821/4221/files/1.jpg?v=1707486871" alt="Description of the image">
